reviewText: Ok.  It  may be that my expectations were at fault.  I was expecting something more in the vein of Ilsa the She Wolf of the SS.  Basically,  this is low budget fetish porn.  Michelle Young spends a lot of time masturbating,  which is shown in full detail.  There is a simulated sex rape scene  and some S&M bondage stuff.  The Nazi uniforms are East German military surplus with some Nazi insignia attached.  There's not a lot here,  no real plot to follow.  The role of the police detective is poorly acted and seems to have been written as a means of plot exposition via rambling soliliquies.  Another character in "Nazi"  uniform shows up without explanation.  If you like fetish porn with graphic female masturbation scenes,  this one's for you.  If you require even the thinnest plot in order to enjoy a movie,  keep looking.

Complete garbage. This will have to rank in the top three of the worst movie, if you want to call it that, ever and I mean ever made. I feel sorry for the landfill that this thing ended up in because it will contaminate it.
OMG, to think I paid $10 for this. It would be an insult to my garbage can to throw it away. I'm going to dig a hole and bury it. BEWARE, you've been warned!!
I know I ordered and old movie, so I was expecting a great picture, or sound. but it is worth what I paid for.
